{"tid":1649921,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"銀髮警總靜坐48 你地就掛住屌蛋糕撚 唔怪得輸啦","createTime":"2019-10-12T19:00:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-12T19:08:41.000Z","uid":149607,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"90a5f1e570270bf3b85b2a5eb125db30dd597a20","tid":1649921,"uid":149607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T19:00:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />年輕人/連登仔係咪都係咁 <br />\n講就凶狠 做就毓民<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">醒呀<br />\n6月9 號到依家 所有烈士同被捕既手足名單洗唔洗係你天生板用紅字寫滿先記得呀？</span>"},{"pid":"b5a8005f1d62bedd4d957e8d293a977b406c1eab","tid":1649921,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T19:00:49.000Z","msg":"push<br />\n<br />\n[品蔥建議] [拋磚引玉] 如何偽裝成一名合格的&ldquo;愛國港人&rdquo;（藍絲）？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1648664\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1648664</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"4fba97fb253728aed4ebce91109845d482fb293b","tid":1649921,"uid":149607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T19:01:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />新屋嶺都準備2.0啦<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">你地準備緊d乜呀</span></span>"},{"pid":"e516d7c3ca392547f92a9fb2f8e8b2fe5f1f978b","tid":1649921,"uid":135349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T19:01:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WiT7Bac.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWiT7Bac.jpg&h=2f01dffd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"219a9814717e2c537e140e5d381814cf6a8b0ca1","tid":1649921,"uid":54959,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T19:03:46.000Z","msg":"啲老人家真係慘，絕食兩日都唔夠一個mk 蛋糕嚟"},{"pid":"a721aca9ae32dee17bae53556d2099c57cad3e69","tid":1649921,"uid":149607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T19:05:31.000Z","msg":"各大行動組唔該懸崖勒馬<br />\n諗清楚我地到底要做乜 唔好帶頭講唔撈<br />\n你地一句唔撈係為左發洩唔該收返<br />\n想佢地反思都一樣收返<br />\n唔醒既點都唔會醒<br />\n但唔好拋棄默默堅持不懈既同路人<br />\n佢地見到你地停手佢地隨之都可能卻步<br />\n因為有你有我先有大家<br />\n唔好帶頭唔撈 我見到連鎖反應黎緊<br />\n報狗車扮狗同埋哨兵個d都跟住你地咁樣做<br />\n隨時害更多人<br />\n咁樣講一句 隨時仲大負面影響過班蛋糕撚<br />\n<br />\n請各位 做任何野前 都要<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">三思</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab7f0b2bb527ccd824461c671da5aebcba1801d8","tid":1649921,"uid":149607,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"219a9814717e2c537e140e5d381814cf6a8b0ca1","tid":1649921,"uid":54959,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T19:03:46.000Z","msg":"啲老人家真係慘，絕食兩日都唔夠一個mk 蛋糕嚟"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T19:06:40.000Z","msg":"班長輩手足仲靜坐抗議緊<br />\n都未黎得切follow up 咩事 <br />\n就見到大家咁既樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f9a2f1a06c89d982f3aedfe23885249fb904168","tid":1649921,"uid":194399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T19:08:41.000Z","msg":"成班花生友"}]}